# Portfolio — dev server cleanup

This repo uses classic Vite (`npm run dev` / `npm run preview`). Servers must be stopped after Agent browser checks.

## Cleanup command

```powershell
powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File scripts/stop-preview.ps1
```

Stops listeners on ports 4173–4180 and 5173.

## Workflow

1. One preview at a time — port **4173** (or `5173` for dev).
2. After verification, run `stop-preview.ps1` before finishing.
3. For production checks, use **https://timothy-yap.pages.dev/** instead of spawning preview when possible.

See also user rule `dev-server-auto-cleanup.mdc`.
